/web.archive.org/web/20121107015551/http://www.amazon.com/Bourne-Identity-Widescreen-Extended-Edition/dp/B00023B1LC }}</ref>，另一个是满屏加长版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Bourne-Identity-Full-Screen-Extended/dp/B00023B1LM/ |title=The Bourne Identity (Full Screen Extended Edition) (2002) |accessdate=2013-09-11 |publisher=Amazon |archivedate=2011-11-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111130160436/http://www.amazon.com/Bourne-Identity-Full-Screen-Extended/dp/B00023B1LM }}</ref>。其中增加了对马特·达蒙的采访，删除镜头，不同的电影开头和结局，有关中央情报局和失忆症的資訊以及领事馆打斗戏段的纪录片。这个版本结局显示伯恩在寻找玛丽的过程中崩溃了，醒来时阿博特站在他旁边，请他回归中央情报局。不过两个版本都没有提供之前珍藏版里包含的评论音轨。影片还于2005年8月30日针对[[索尼電腦娛樂|索尼]]的[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]发行了[[通用媒體光碟|UMD]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/The-Bourne-Identity-UMD-PSP/dp/B0009WK5CW |title=The Bourne Identity [UMD for PSP] (2002) |publisher=Amazon |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233433/http://www.amazon.com/The-Bourne-Identity-UMD-PSP/dp/B0009WK5CW |archive-date=2013-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后于2007年7月24日发行了[[HD_DVD|HD DVD]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/The-Bourne-Identity-HD-DVD/dp/B000QEIOTO |title=The Bourne Identity [HD DVD] (2002) |publisher=Amazon |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2012-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930081724/http://www.amazon.com/The-Bourne-Identity-HD-DVD/dp/B000QEIOTO }}</ref>。在《神鬼認證：最後通牒》发行DVD后，《伯恩的身份》、《伯恩的霸权》和《神鬼認證：最後通牒》于2009年1月一起发行了三部曲套装[[蓝光光碟|蓝光光碟]]<ref name="Blu-rayTrilogy">{{cite news|last=Ault |first=Susanne |url=http://www.videobusiness.com/article/CA6635299.html |title=Universal bundles Blu-ray catalog titles |work=Video Business |date=2009-02-06 |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214202502/http://www.videobusiness.com/article/CA6635299.html |archivedate=2009-02-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Trilogy-Identity-Supremacy-Ultimatum-Blu-ray/dp/B001LPWGE6/ |title=