== 续集 ==
{{see also|谍影重重系列电影}}
2004年上映的《[[伯恩的霸权|伯恩的霸权]]》是本片的续集，该片也获得了影评人和观众类似的正面评价<ref name="RT2">{{cite web|work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixter |title=The Bourne Supremacy (2004) |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bourne_supremacy/ |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605181548/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bourne_supremacy/ |archivedate=2013-06-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-supremacy |title=The Bourne Supremacy Reviews |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-10-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013170201/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-supremacy |deadurl=no }}</ref>，不过也有影评人批评片中手提攝影机的拍摄风格让动作戏很难看清楚<ref name="HRUltimatum">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/bourne-ultimatum-158258 |title=The Bourne Ultimatum |work=The Hollywood Reporter |format=Registration Required |accessdate=2009-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011040523/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/bourne-ultimatum-158258 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片由[[保羅·葛林葛瑞斯|保羅·葛林葛瑞斯]]执导，马特·达蒙继续出演同一角色。2007年的《[[神鬼認證：最後通牒|神鬼認證：最後通牒]]》是本片的第二部续集，同样由保羅·葛林葛瑞斯导演，马特·达蒙主演，影片也像前作一样获得了影评人和观众的好评，并且其摄影也受到了与《伯恩的霸权》类似的批评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bourne_ultimatum/ |title=The Bourne Ultimatum (2007) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixter |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605190035/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/bourne_ultimatum/ |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-ultimatum |title=The Bourne Ultimatum Reviews, Ratings, Credits |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025065246/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-ultimatum }}</ref><ref name="TimeCrit">{{cite news|last=Corliss |first=Richard |url=http://content.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1649187,00.html |title=The Bourne Ultimatum: A Macho Fantasy |work=Time |date=2007-08-02 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-08-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824183658/http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0%2C8599%2C1649187%2C00.html }}</ref>。

2012年上映的《[[神鬼認證4|神鬼認證4]]》是这一系列的第4部作品，不过达蒙和葛林葛瑞斯都没有参与这个项目，而是由[[東尼·格萊|東尼·格萊]]出任导演，[[杰瑞米·雷纳|杰瑞米·雷纳]]扮演男主角，影片所获评价褒贬不一，但总体上还是趋于正面。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/10/11/no-matt-damon-in-bourne-legacy/ |title=No Matt Damon in 'Bourne Legacy': Report |author=Labrecque, Jeff |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2010-10-11 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-02-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204145818/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/10/11/no-matt-damon-in-bourne-legacy/ |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/204976/wtf-matt-damon-out-of-the-bourne-legacy |title=WTF?! Matt Damon Out of The Bourne Legacy |author=Gina Serpe |work=E! Online |date=2010-10-11 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120930190732/http://www.eonline.com/news/204976/wtf-matt-damon-out-of-the-bourne-legacy }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-legacy |title=The Bourne Legacy Reviews |publisher=CBS |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-11-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103013329/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-bourne-legacy }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_bourne_legacy/ |title=The Bourne Legacy (2012) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixter |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-09-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905132155/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_bourne_legacy/ }}</ref>系列第5部作品《[[神鬼認證：傑森包恩|神鬼認證：傑森包恩]]》在2016年上映，口碑一般<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jason_bourne/ | title=Jason Bourne (2016) | website=Rotten Tomatoes | publisher=Flixter | accessdate=2018-08-28 | archive-date=2016-07-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729010910/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jason_bourne/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，不過票房開出紅盤<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/10/10/box-office-jason-bourne-was-a-big-hit-thanks-to-a-small-budget/|title=Box Office: 'Jason Bourne' Was A Big Hit Thanks To A Small Budget|first=Scott|last=Mendelson|work=[[福布斯|Forbes]]|date=2016-10-10|accessdate=2016-10-12|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217053201/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/10/10/box-office-jason-bourne-was-a-big-hit-thanks-to-a-small-budget/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

